preference.name: CAE_file_upload_default_conflict_resolution_option
preference.preference_description: Defines the options available when there is a name conflict while uploading a file from a dataset. The system provides an interactive dialog while the other options are automatically applied. Valid Values: Upload: This option will automatically upload the file.Versioning rules of named references will apply to archiving. Rename and Upload: This option will rename the file and upload in the defined dataset. Skip: This option will skip the file and not upload it into Teamcenter.
